name: Sophia Lee
details: Sophia is a certified fitness trainer with over 5 years of experience. She specializes in yoga, mindfulness, and helping clients achieve their personal fitness goals.
otherInfo: Sophia is passionate about holistic fitness and believes in integrating physical, mental, and emotional well-being.

name: Michael Brown
details: Michael is a professional strength and conditioning coach with 8+ years of experience. He specializes in weight training and muscle building.
otherInfo: Michael believes in progressive overload principles and customizes plans for his clients to achieve long-term fitness goals.

name: Emma Davis
details: Ava is a Pilates expert with a passion for helping people improve their posture and flexibility. She has been teaching Pilates for over 6 years.
otherInfo: Ava is dedicated to helping her clients achieve a strong core and overall balance through consistent Pilates practice.

name: Isabella Wilson
details: Daniel is a certified CrossFit coach who focuses on high-intensity functional training. He has been training individuals and groups for over a decade.
otherInfo: Daniel designs training regimens to maximize performance while minimizing the risk of injury.

name: Oliver Martinez
details: Emma is a certified Zumba instructor who brings energy and fun to every workout. Her goal is to make fitness enjoyable for everyone.
otherInfo: Emma loves combining fitness with music to create an exciting and motivating experience for her clients.

name: low Brown
details: Oliver is a professional personal trainer with expertise in functional fitness and weight loss. He has a decade of experience helping clients achieve sustainable health goals.
otherInfo: Oliver takes a holistic approach to fitness, emphasizing mental and physical well-being in his training programs.
